{
  "stem": "964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because there was-- it was very common that Poles joined the Germans, helped them out in the-- as volunteers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they were Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We're not Poles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I said, I'm going to tell them that we are Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You two stay outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I'm not coming out, split, run wherever you can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were standing at the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm in one place, the [NON-ENGLISH] was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jakob comes out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we saw a piece of paper that we were to get the-- the-- the food, and another was where we should go sleep.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he told us a story that that commandant said, look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you would have been Germans, I can incorporate you in our-- in our other unit, and they're going to go to front, and you're going to be fighting like any other Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But since you are Poles, I cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come back in 10 days, or seven days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They told us to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe some of the company-- he describe us-- we should describe how the company-- what kind of logo the company had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every company has a different logo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he made the logo, he made it upside down, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they wouldn't have recognized it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, maybe somebody will come along and ask for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So meantime, you have here food and you have where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came out, and-- and-- and we got-- when he came out, we got together and we decide, what do we do now?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we decided not to go to sleep in the place where he send us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because somebody may-- may-- may recognize us or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you say, OK, these guys are over there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go get them.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
